    "We report the F1 and the standard error averaged across five prompt templates for all the datasets.",
    "Bonito-using Q-LoRA (Dettmers et al., 2023).",
    "When further adapting Mistral-7B P3 and Llama 2 7B P3, we fine-tune the same Q-LoRA adapter on the supervision sources instead of merging and reinitializing the adapters.",
